Australia has posted a significant total on the board despite losing two wickets within the powerplay. The partnership between Tahlia McGrath and Grace Harris was outstanding. Renuka and Deepti picked up two wickets each. Can Australia continue their winning streak? Will India be able to chase this down? Stay tuned for the exciting run chase.

Annabel Sutherland to Renuka Singh Thakur. Length ball, outside off stump on the back foot pulling, mis-timed to deep backward square leg for 1 run, fielded by Perry. Australia win a thrilling close match and have qualified for the semi-final. The Indian openers failed to give a good start in the chase. Harmanpreet and Deepti managed to build a solid partnership to get them back into it, but it was not enough to chase the target. Sutherland and Molineux picked up two wickets each. Sophie Molineux is the Player of the Match.
